      • compile

        public static ExpressionNode compile(String expressionNode)
        Compiles the given expression node in an ExpressionNode instance, appropriate for your type. Note: If this expression node already was compiled then the cached instance that will be returned.
        Parameters:
        expressionNode - the desired expression node
        Returns:
        an compiled instance or null, if the expression node not is a field, method or array
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the given expression node is null
